name: Cryptic. Fig°1
description: ☣ 'Cryptic. Fig°1' | 2021 | Chris Kore @chriskore www.chriskore.com ☣ 'Cryptic' is the series of AI artworks that exists on the edge of Uncanny Valley and Machinery Misinterpretation. There is an idea crossing Simulation and Multiverse theories saying that our present universe has appeared by an error. That some of the most basic features of our particular reality are indeed mere accidents—a random throw of the cosmic dice. ☣ Fig°1 is a first creature and citizen through the looking-glass. ☣ This AI experiment will last for a year revealing various rare and super rare representatives of each AI tribe. ☣
